products.title: XiMonth Sleep Stickers for Stress Relief & Relaxation Aroma Patches Bedtime & Travel
products.body_html:
XiMonth Sleep Stickers – Care for Body & Mind, Relieve Stress, Relaxation & Better Sleep

Discover XiMonth Sleep Stickers, a natural aromatherapy solution designed to calm the body and mind so you can sleep better. Infused with Apple Extract, Valerian, Hops, Lavender, Cedar and Sweet Orange, these aroma patches deliver gentle, soothing fragrance to ease tension, relieve stress and support a deep, restorative night’s sleep. Ideal for bedtime routines, travel, shift workers, or anyone needing quick relaxation after screen fatigue or a long day.

How to Use:

  1. Clean and dry the skin where you will apply the sticker (chest, inner wrist, collarbone or clothing).

  2. Open the packet and peel the sticker from the backing.

  3. Apply the adhesive side firmly to skin or fabric—avoid broken or irritated skin.

  4. Leave on for up to 8–12 hours as needed (remove sooner if irritation occurs).

  5. Dispose of the sticker after use. For best results, use 30–60 minutes before bedtime or when you need immediate relaxation.
    Note: Do not apply directly over cuts, rashes, or sensitive eye area. Patch test on inner forearm for sensitive skin.

Specifications:

  • Product: XiMonth Sleep Stickers (Aromatherapy Patches)

  • Type: Body Care Kit — Sleep & Stress Relief Stickers

  • Ingredients: Apple extract, Valerian, Hops, Lavender, Cedar, Sweet Orange

  • Product Size: 7.5 x 7.5 cm (per sticker)

  • Color Classification / Pack Options: 12pcs / 24pcs

  • Cosmetics for Special Purposes: No

  • Relieves stress & calms the body & mind.

  • Promotes deeper, more restful sleep and quicker relaxation.

  • Natural herbal aroma blend — no heavy chemicals.

  • Easy, mess-free application — perfect for travel & bedside use.
